version_description: Newest session, venue and event information.
Newest session, venue and event information.
Newest session details and bug fixes.

Show remembered sessions more prominently in schedule.
Updated session information.

+ Updated for Google I/O 2017
+ Get the latest event details and updates in the Feed
+ Read important information about the Event, Travel details, and FAQ
+ Reserve seats for events ahead of schedule

What's New:
Updated for Google I/O 2018:
+ Includes the newest schedule information.
+ Bug fixes and performance improvements.
+ Minor cosmetic updates to the session detail screen.

+ Fixed an issue where times in the Agenda screen didn't display correctly in non-PDT time zones.
+ Fixed a crash when unable to access certain Google user metadata.
+ Fixed a crash on iPads when trying to share sessions.
+ Minor cosmetic updates to the Info > Event screen.
+ Adds Keynote tags to Keynote events.
- Fixed a layout issue where some announcements in the Home screen had their last line truncated.

- Fixed a crash when that occurred when navigating away from Explore mode with unresolved promises.
- Fixed an issue where session updates were processed on the main thread, causing the app to stutter.
- Fixed an issue where navigating away from Explore would cause the rest of the app to drop frames.
- Fixed a layout issue that prevented title cards in the Home screen from displaying correctly.
